description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
- Chefchaouen, Morocco
- Valparaíso, Chile
- Cinque Terre, Italy
- Copenhagen, Denmark
- Santorini, Greece
- Odaiba, Tokyo, Japan
- Procida, Italy
- Burano, Italy
- Rothenburg ob der Tauber, Germany
- Curaçao, Kingdom of the Netherlands
name: Colorful Town
